  ('investigation-d5dfc642-moex-00066', 'investigation-d5dfc642', 'investigation-d5dfc642-moex-113-8d1d3a67', 'sub-investigation-d5dfc642-01', NULL, 'essay', '審判中，檢察官提出被告甲在警詢時的自白筆錄及錄音檔案作為證據之
