  ('investigation-d5dfc642-moex-00072', 'investigation-d5dfc642', 'investigation-d5dfc642-moex-113-916530c6', 'sub-investigation-d5dfc642-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲於晚上與友人喝酒餐聚，回家後倒頭大睡，睡了 6 小時後起床聽聞 A
